		<div id=\"lingua-list\"><h4>This post is also available in:</h4><dl>	<dt>Fran\x{e7}ais: </dt>		<dd><a href=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/2009/06/08/11644/\">Gabon : R\x{e9}action des blogueurs africains \x{e0} la mort du Pr\x{e9}sident Omar Bongo...</a></dd>	<dt>Malagasy: </dt>		<dd><a href=\"http://mg.globalvoicesonline.org/2009/06/09/2532/\">Gabon: Manodidina ny fahafatesan&#39;ny Filoha Omar Bongo...</a></dd>	<dt>bahasa Indonesia: </dt>		<dd><a href=\"http://id.globalvoicesonline.org/2009/06/1390/\">Gabon: Kematian Presiden Omar Bongo...</a></dd></dl></div>			
